OL,3,C'We can't run away from it' - Tandy
OL,4,Creacts to WRU cuts announcement
OL,6,FWales' head coach Steve Tandy has
OL,7,Freacted publicly for the first time,
OL,8,Fsince the WRU planned to cut the
OL,9,Fnumber of professional club sides in
OL,10,FWales from four to three as soon as
OL,11,Fpossible.
OL,13,FIt is currently unclear what the
OL,14,Fidentity of the three teams will be,
OL,15,Fbut it is understood that there will
OL,16,Fbe one based in Cardiff, one in East
OL,17,FWales and one in West Wales.
