OL,3,C'We can't run away from it' - Tandy
OL,4,Creacts to WRU cuts announcement
OL,6,FAt a press conference on Tuesday (28
OL,7,FOctober) he praised the players for
OL,8,Fstaying "connected" and being "there
OL,9,Ffor each other."
OL,11,FHe said: "We can't run away from
OL,12,Fit...it's (a) big moment but
OL,13,Fultimately the boys have responded
OL,14,Freally really well...they're human,
OL,15,Fthey have got families and as coaches,
OL,16,Fas parents, and as husbands, you
OL,17,Funderstand that...I think if you have
OL,18,Fempathy and you can talk about it, you
OL,19,Fcan focus the mind."
