OL,3,C'We can't run away from it' - Tandy
OL,4,Creacts to WRU cuts announcement
OL,6,FIn August, the WRU said that radical
OL,7,Fchange was needed to save the game
OL,8,Ffrom its steady decline. But, after
OL,9,Ffurious backlash from players and
OL,10,Fsupporters, they were forced to
OL,11,Fretreat from that position.
OL,13,FThe optimal solution proposed by new
OL,14,FDirector of Rugby Dave Reddin was
OL,15,Fhalving the number of professional
OL,16,Fteams in Wales, consolidating top
OL,17,Ftalent and resources into two clubs.
OL,18,FBut after a consultation process, the
OL,19,FUnion has decided on three teams.
