OL,3,C'We can't run away from it' - Tandy
OL,4,Creacts to WRU cuts announcement
OL,6,FOspreys player Jac Morgan previously
OL,7,Fsaid he would leave Welsh rugby if the
OL,8,FOspreys were to get cut.
OL,10,FAddressing this at the press
OL,11,Fconference he said: "I love the
OL,12,FOspreys, I love playing there, the
OL,13,Fboys, the coaches...the news only came
OL,14,Fout on Friday (24th October) so the
OL,15,Fbig focus now for myself is this
OL,16,Fcampaign and we will see how
OL,17,Feverything else goes."
