OL,3,C'We can't run away from it' - Tandy
OL,4,Creacts to WRU cuts announcement
OL,6,FMorgan has been selected to captain
OL,7,Fthe Welsh side as they head into their
OL,8,FAutumn internationals campaign,
OL,9,Fagainst Argentina on Sunday, November
OL,10,F9.
OL,12,FHe said: "We have got to focus now for
OL,13,Fthe upcoming games and this upcoming
OL,14,Fcampaign...we are not just
OL,15,Frepresenting Wales are representing
OL,16,Four nations our communities."
